4560.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4560.description: On the eve of the eclipse, Aang's anxiety gets the better of him. His dreams become nightmares, and soon he can no longer tell dream from reality.

4561.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4561.description: It is the Day of Black Sun and the group meets up with the invasion force."The day has finally arrived and Aang is ready to take on the Fire Lord. But they soon realize that things aren't going to go according to plan, and their surprise attack isn't so unexpected." Part 2 is "The Day of Black Sun, Part 2: The Eclipse."

4562.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4562.description: Patrick has a coupon for free ice cream, but he'll have to get to the store if he wants to use it! // Krabs buys Squidward's art, but to make a profit on his purchase he'll have to get the artist out of the picture!

4563.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4563.description: When a prehistoric Sponge is unfrozen, he causes chaos all over town - and only SpongeBob can communicate with him! // When a flock of clams descend on Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob has to get them out before they ruin the whole town!

4564.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4564.description: Feeling guilty for turning April's father into a mutant bat, the Turtles perfect a retro-mutagen to help him. Unfortunately, things get worse when Baxter Stockman threatens to mutate April.

4565.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4565.description: Raph is worried about Casey's ability to handle big mutant threats...when they meet Slash again and discover he has a partner of his own: THE NEWTRALIZER!

4566.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4566.description: When Shifu's con-man father comes back into town, Po finds himself in the middle.

4567.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4567.description: Po is excited when he discovers a kung fu prodigy, but starts to worry when people seem to prefer the new kid to their beloved Dragon Warrior.

4568.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4568.description: The penguin's habitat must undergo a serious repair. So Alice calls in Gus, a strong willed contractor. The penguins must stop Gus before he unearths their secret HQ. // When King Julien wishes on the Gimme Gimme Star, he gets more than he asked for.

4569.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4569.description: Julien suspects a plot to overthrow or kill him is being orchestrated by Maurice. // Burt discovers a love for painting. He's very talented. Kowalski's blueprints for a quantum accelerator get mixed in with his paintings and end up in the museum.

4570.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4570.description: SpongeBob and Patrick get hooked on the latest fad - flying your own brain like a tiny drone! // When SpongeBob & Patrick play Mermaidman and Barnacleboy, it's all fun and games until their sworn enemies arrive!

4571.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4571.description: When SpongeBob thinks he's allergic to his pineapple, Squidward offers to help find him a new home. // Squidward is getting a nose job at the local hospital, and SpongeBob tags along as moral support.

4572.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4572.description: SpongeBob learns that "imitation is the sincerest form of flattery" - too bad no one told him how to stop! // When worms move in to SpongeBob's holes, it's up to him to hide his disgusting new friends from everyone else.

4573.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4573.description: Nella and Trinket accidently agree to attend both Garrett and Minatori's sleepovers on the same night. // Garrett and Blaine disobey the rules and sneak out at night to see a fantastical star.

4574.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4574.description: Blaine's fancy cousin Olivia visits and questions Nella's ability to be both a princess and a knight. // When Nella loses a knightly contest, she's determined to improve by practicing.

4575.title: Bubble Guppies
4575.description: For Clam Day, the Bubble Guppies decide to throw a party for Clam and invite his cousin Sam. But before they can send Sam an invitation, they need to learn all about how the mail works.

4576.title: Bubble Guppies
4576.description: The Bubble Guppies explore different kinds of ball games as they get ready for their big game of Fishketball! Join Team Guppies to help them practice bouncing, throwing, catching and playing together as a team.

4577.title: Dora the Explorer
4577.description: Dora remembers the first time she met her friend Backpack. Backpack is helping Dora carry her books back to the Library. Can they reach the Library before it closes?

4578.title: Dora the Explorer
4578.description: Dora and Boots offer to help Mama Bugga Bugga bring a giant cookie home to feed her babies.

4579.title: Rusty Rivets
4579.description: Rusty builds a robot version of himself, so he can do two things at once. // Rusty and Ruby build a robotic buddy for Botasaur, a Kittybot!

4580.title: Rusty Rivets
4580.description: Ruby wants to see a comet fly by, and Rusty will do everything in his power to make sure his friend's wish comes true! // Rusty and Ruby race to fix a leaking underwater oil pipeline before it pollutes the lake and makes it uninhabitable.

4581.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
4581.description: When Crusher tries to cheat at a carnival game, he accidentally strands himself and Pickle on a giant rocket! Now it’s up to Blaze and AJ to rescue the two trucks before their runaway rocket crashes into the garbage dump.

4582.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
4582.description: Gabby, Blaze and AJ are out in the wilderness when they get a call, Blaze's friends have come down with a sickness called the Sneezles! Our heroes must race back to Axle City to bring the sick trucks the medicine oil they need.

4583.title: PAW Patrol
4583.description: We see a flashback of how Rubble became a member of the Paw Patrol! // When Wally the Walrus gets tangled in an old fishing net, Ryder and the Paw Patrol need to get him to the surface and back to shore safely.

4584.title: PAW Patrol
4584.description: Farmer Yumi's carrots are disappearing and she calls Ryder and the Paw Patrol for help. // Katie is excited to be entering one of the Paw Patrol pups into a puppy grooming competition "Puptacular" in the next town.

4585.title: PAW Patrol
4585.description: Ryder and the PAW Patrol clean up a small oil spill in the water near Adventure Bay. They must plug the hole in the ship, clean up the oil and save the animals and fish in Adventure Bay./When Adventure Bay’s famous statue ends up at the bottom of the Bay, Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to help Mayor Goodway and find a clever way to bring it back!

4586.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4586.description: A new neighbor moves in and becomes Squidward’s best friend. // SpongeBob helps Squidward prepare for a date.

4587.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4587.description: Patrick's big sister Samantha comes for a visit. // Sandy and Plankton bond over their shared love.

4588.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4588.description: Squidward gets hurt on the job when he takes a nap during work and a shelf buries him. He threatens to report the Krusty Krab to the authorities unless Mr. Krabs waits on him hand and foot. But how long will Krabs let him get away with it? / Mr. Krabs and Plankton set aside their differences in the face of a common enemy. The popular new "Flabby Patty" restaurant is stealing their business!

4589.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4589.description: The penguins have had enough of the crazy lemurs 24 hour parting! They hack into the zoo habitat schematic and successfully transfer the lemurs to the petting zoo. // The penguins journey to the bottom of the Atlantic for 100 year-old preserved herring.

4590.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4590.description: When Kowalski's ray designed to freshen spoiled food accidentally hits Skipper before falling down a storm drain, the leader is turned into a baby penguin, albeit retaining much of Skipper's adult personality. // After learning of Savio's escape from Hoboken on a TV news report, the penguins organize an effort to protect the zoo from the vengeful boa.

4591.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4591.description: Po is distraught when he learns that everyone in town has been invited to a fancy dinner party except for him, due to his slovenly behavior and table manners. Will Shifu and the Five be able to teach Po proper etiquette AND foil the attack of evil Temutai and his army? Not likely.

4592.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4592.description: When Shifu's ex-girlfriend, Mei Ling, visits the Jade Palace, Po decides to try and get them back together, despite the fact Mei Ling is now Shifu's most hated enemy.

4593.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4593.description: Mikey discovers that a new mutant is trying to attack and capture people using living pizzas, but he struggles to convince the others who don't believe him.

4594.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4594.description: Leo, worried about Karai, tries to convince the others to rescue her, while a master thief steals Shredder's helmet, and it falls into the Turtles' unsuspecting hands.

4595.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4595.description: Mr. Krabs and Plankton have been business rivals and bitter enemies for longer than anyone can remember. But one day, Mr. Krabs reveals that they were not always this way. There was a time when the two rivals were best friends.

4596.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4596.description: Mr. Krab's old fry cook pays a special visit to the Krusty Krab. SpongeBob is in awe of his predecessor, who has since become a world renowned chef following his departure from Krabs' restaurant. // Tales of the boogeyman sends SpongeBob into panic. Every dark corner in his house could be a potential hiding place for the infamous monster.

4597.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4597.description: SpongeBob finds a nasty sea urchin living in the Krusty Krab, and tries everything to force it out. // After getting his groceries stolen, Squidward convinces SpongeBob and Sandy to teach him karate.

4598.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4598.description: Po befriends a band of dancers, unaware they're actually a band of traveling thieves.

4599.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4599.description: When the Furious 5 are all out of town and the Jade Palace is attacked, Po only has his dad and two old people to help him.

4600.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4600.description: Lemmy the robot returns from Mars. Unknowingly a space squid has stowed away in his chest cavity. // Careless Alice over chlorinates the otter habitat and Marlene’s fur is bleached. Her new look captivates the attention of the other zoo animals.

4601.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4601.description: The zoo animals are suffering a heat wave. The penguins have a plan to beat the heat, but they need Alice out of the way. With her gone, they get to work. // Private is smitten with the zoo nurse. The only way he can see her is if he gets injured.

4602.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4602.description: Tiger Claw returns and intends to destroy the Turtles at any cost.

4603.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4603.description: Mikey discovers that a new mutant is trying to attack and capture people using living pizzas, but he struggles to convince the others who don't believe him.

4604.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4604.description: SpongeBob and Patrick try to help Sandy rid her Tree Dome of fleas. // When Patrick accidentally takes SpongeBob’s donut he is wracked with guilt over his heinous crime. // SpongeBob battles a persistent speck of food that is on a plate.

4605.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4605.description: Plankton creates a gas that turns everyone at the Krusty Krab into babies. // After being enrolled in a chef exchange program, SpongeBob switches places with a snooty French chef from a high-end restaurant.

4606.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4606.description: It’s Picture Day for the Boating School Year Book, and SpongeBob has spent all morning getting ready for it. Now all he has to do is make it to Boating School without getting dirty. // When Patrick eats his weight in Krabby Patties without paying, Mr. Krabs puts him to work in the restaurant. // SpongeBob’s parents are missing. All clues of their whereabouts point to his nefarious cousin Blackjack, the family bully who used to torment SpongeBob when they were little.

4607.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4607.description: A rash of thefts in the Valley of Peace has the villagers in uproar and things only get worse when the culprit appears to be... Monkey?

4608.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4608.description: Po's Kung Fu hero, Kwan the Unkillable, comes to the Valley of Peace and appears to be a feeble old man. Po agrees to stage a fight to help him get back on top. But Kwan may not be as weak as he looks.

4609.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4609.description: The penguins are inspired after witnessing a good deed executed by a zoo patron. So they set out to perform their own good deeds - penguin's style. When things don't work out as planned, a domino of bad events requires fixing. // While Mort and Private stop to liberate Cheezy Bitz from the zoo vending machine they are both sucked in. Each attempt to escape fails and their only hope is to be rescued, but everyone is searching for them outside of the zoo.

4610.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4610.description: It's game night and the penguins are playing hot potato with a live bomb. // According to the penguin's intel, the sewer rats are up to something BIG. They need an undercover operative. But who is rat-like enough to pull off such a mission? Mort.

4611.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4611.description: Second part to "The Day of Black Sun, Part 1: The Invasion". The eclipse has started and the gang only has a few minutes to get into an underground bunker and find and defeat Ozai. Zuko confront his father and learn about his mother's banishment while Aang, Sokka and Toph fight Azula and her Dai Li agents.

4612.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4612.description: The gang leaves the Fire Nation, humbled and embarrassed by the failure of the invasion. They head to the Western Air Temple. However, unknown to them, Zuko is also following them in the hope of joining their group to teach Aang firebending.

4613.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4613.description: While trying to wrestle open the cap off of a tube of toothpaste SpongeBob accidentally punches himself in the face leaving behind a hideous black eye. // Plankton has brainwashed Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy! With the dynamic duo under Plankton’s control, he orders them to wreak havoc on the Krusty Krab. It’s up to SpongeBob SquarePants and his trusty spatula to save the day!

4614.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4614.description: Instead of getting on the ship headed for summer camp, SpongeBob and Patrick accidentally board a ship full of prisoners on their way to jail on Inferno Island. // SpongeBob and Pat stow away on one of Sandy’s extreme wilderness expeditions. But when they get accidentally left behind, they must band together in order to survive in the wild.

4615.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4615.description: While researching his family tree SpongeBob discovers that he was related to the great Western hero, and famous chili-slinger, SpongeBuck.

4616.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4616.description: Leo, worried about Karai, tries to convince the others to rescue her, while a master thief steals Shredder's helmet, and it falls into the Turtles' unsuspecting hands.

4617.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4617.description: Raph's hot-headed impulsiveness lands him in deep trouble when he accidentally damages a machine that forces him to switch minds with a Kraang.

4618.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4618.description: Master Chao visits the valley to oversee a Tournament. Shifu is convinced that Po and Master Chao want to replace him. Shifu's old enemy, Pai Mei, arrives in the middle of the tournament and threatens to destroy Shifu.

4619.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4619.description: Master Yao returns to the Jade Palace and announces that he's offering the Valley of Peace a one-day 'Wonder and Wisdom Exchange'. Anyone who brings him a new wonder will be allowed to ask him a single question.

4620.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4620.description: The lemur habitat acquires a new resident, Clemson, and King Julien loves to order him around. Maurice enjoys not having to work, but Mort remains highly suspicious of Clemson, he knows that he is up to something evil. // Kowalski's attempt to super charge his brain backfires and now he's dumber than mud. His lack of intellect starts to comprise the troop's missions. Skipper, Private and Rico must find a cure for him before he hurts someone.

4621.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4621.description: Private hones in on his cuteness factor and BOOSH! Any witness or potential threat is instantly disabled - adorability has been weaponized. // In the haste of a zoo animal meeting, King Julien and Skipper are agreed to switch places for a single day.

4622.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4622.description: Private's quirky Uncle Nigel pops in for a quick visit from across the pond. // The boys intercept a fax with cartographic news; Maurice has only 24 hours to live. In order to make Maurice's assumed final day comfortable, the entire zoo bands together.

4623.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4623.description: SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs turn an old submarine into a mobile Krusty Krab. Not to be undone by his competitor’s new gimmick, Plankton responds with his own traveling Chum Bucket. // When Patrick and SpongeBob discover they have clashing views on cleanliness, their disagreement blows up into an epic battle. Is it possible for a soap-lover like SpongeBob to ever be friends with a dirt-monger like Patrick?

4624.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4624.description: When SpongeBob tries to spend some quality time with his friends, he just ends up being a nuisance to everyone instead. They all tell him to go away, so with a heavy heart, SpongeBob decides to do just that.

4625.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4625.description: Squidward is rushed to the hospital when SpongeBob accidentally slams the door on Squidward’s face. He undergoes surgery to have his face fixed to look normal again – but things don’t go exactly as planned. // A very windy day in Bikini Bottom is blowing air through SpongeBob’s holes resulting in a chorus of pretty flute-like sounds. This attracts all the local Jellyfish who love the music coming out of SpongeBob.
